thread.title: Jason
thread.title_full: Fast Cover Travel Insurance reviewed by Jason

author: Jason
title: Jason
text: I read through all of the fine print and the PDS and this one is definitely a much beeter insurance. It covers more than most of them out there and has minimal to no excess. There are many extras you can add that are not needed for most people which means you are not wasting money on something you don't need. I would recommend this one to anyone needing domestic travel throughout Australia.
